data.name: customSqlQuery1.Sql
data.value: select fm.Fee1 as Fee,fm.Fee1 as Fe,fm.FeeDate1 as FeeDate,fm.paymentid as Pay,fm.paymentid as Pay1,fm.paymentid as Pay2,fm.FeeDate1 as Date,fm.Bankname as Bank,fm.Number as Num,fm.*,im.Name as StudentName from FeesMaster fm, InquiryMaster im where im.Id=fm.InquiryId
